---
title: SMHI Weather & Lightning Tracker — Decision Engine
---
flowchart TD
    Start([Request: address + difficulty]) --> Geo{Address in cache?}
    Geo -->|Yes| Diff{Difficulty tier?}
    Geo -->|No| Nom["Nominatim<br/>Nordic-first → global fallback"]
    Nom --> Diff

    Diff -->|🟢 Easy| E1["Map to nearest of 5<br/>preset cities by Haversine"]
    Diff -->|🟡 Medium| M1["Query stations WHERE active=1<br/>Haversine → top 1"]
    Diff -->|🔴 Hard| H1["Top 3 stations<br/>IDW weights = 1/d²"]

    E1 --> Fetch{"Station CSV<br/>in memory?"}
    M1 --> Fetch
    H1 --> Fetch
    Fetch -->|miss| SMHI["GET MetObs CSV<br/>parse + cap 113→100%"]
    Fetch -->|hit| Aggr["Aggregate<br/>daily / monthly / yearly"]
    SMHI --> Aggr

    Aggr --> LGT{Lightning DB seeded?}
    LGT -->|✅ COMPLETED| BBox["SQL bbox filter<br/>uses idx_lightning_coords"]
    LGT -->|⏳ SEEDING/PENDING| Sim["Synthetic model<br/>seasonal × lat × area"]
    BBox --> Hav["Haversine refine<br/>O of n bbox-rows"]
    Hav --> Prob["Compute monthly<br/>probability % + counts"]
    Sim --> Prob

    Prob --> AI{Forecast requested?}
    AI -->|No| Done([📦 JSON response])
    AI -->|GEMINI_API_KEY set| Gem["Gemini 2.5-flash<br/>strict JSON prompt"]
    AI -->|key missing| Stat["Statistical mean + jitter<br/>+ latitude narrative"]
    Gem -->|exception| Stat
    Gem --> Done
    Stat --> Done

